metadata.title: ModParty Bride Beach Bag | Mrs. Burlap Tote Bag | Engagement, Bridal Shower, & Wedding Gift for Bride | Honeymoon Travel Carry On | Large Jute Canvas Carrier
features: CUTE STYLE: These adorable jute beach bags come printed with Mrs and a small heart in a beautiful white script font. Each tote comes with leather handles, a zipper closure, and an inside pocket.
BRIDE GIFT: These are the perfect gift for any bride during her bridal shower! The future Mrs will love using her tote bag at the beach, bachelorette, and honeymoon!
LARGE SIZE: Talk about spacious! Bags are 14"H x 19"W with a 6” gusset. You can carry all your beach essentials with ease.
MATERIAL: 100% Burlap Jute Fabric. Leather Handles.
description: Looking for a bridal shower gift that will stand out? This Mrs. Jute Tote Bag will definitely be a memorable gift for any beach-loving bride! Each tote is made of a burlap jute fabric and leather handles. Conveniently pack all of your beach essentials and keep them from falling out with the zipped closure. Also includes an inside pocket perfect for smaller items such as your phone or keys. Bags are 14"H x 19"W with a 6” gusset.
